      "summary": "EPLB 策略工厂，根据策略类型 ID 选择并实例化对应的负载均衡策略（默认/随机/FlashLB/SwiftBalancer），并触发预热。",
      "tags": ["factory", "eplb", "moe", "dispatch"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "class:eplb/core/policy/policy_factory.py:PolicyFactory",
      "type": "class",
