      "summary": "策略工厂类，通过 generate_policy 按策略类型映射返回相应的 EplbPolicy 子类实例。",
      "tags": ["factory", "eplb", "dispatch", "moe"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:eplb/core/policy/policy_flashlb.py",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "policy_flashlb.py",
      "filePath": "eplb/core/policy/policy_flashlb.py",
      "summary": "FlashLB 专家负载均衡策略实现，基于统计量（均值/方差/协方差）与树形搜索优化专家副本数和 LPT 部署，最小化重部署开销并提升均衡度。",
      "tags": ["eplb", "moe", "load-balancing", "statistics", "optimization"],
      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "综合使用 numpy、scipy 的 linear_sum_assignment 以及 torch，实现增量统计、副本生成与 LPT 装箱优化。"
    },
    {
