      "type": "function",
      "name": "min_max_replica",
      "filePath": "eplb/core/policy/policy_flashlb.py",
      "lineRange": [25, 62],
      "summary": "在给定均值与方差下，使用最小化最大负载策略迭代地为各专家分配可用副本数。",
      "tags": ["eplb", "replica", "load-balancing", "numpy"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
